                 Philadelphia City Treasurer's Office

                 Mission
                 The City Treasurer's Office manages the development and administration
   of the City's debt policies and those of its related agencies and
   coordinates the provision of financial analysis and support to the City
   and its related agencies. It also manages the City's cash resources to
   maximize the limited resources which are available to the municipal
   government to serve the citizens of Philadelphia.

   Contact Information
